   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Verso:"Poseidonios to ?]  greetings. As soon as you read my [letter, order] Tettaphos, of the residents of Lysimachis, [to appear before] us, so that we may investigate the matters on which [he has been accused by Peteur]is, the fuller, if [you please].";Farewell. Year 5, Audnaios 4, Pauni 4.;Recto: [To . . .]ros</ab>
         </div>
